    <div class="item-content">
      <div class="jenkins-button" onclick="showInfo()">Git</div>
      <p>Distributed version control system for tracking changes in source code during software development..</p>
      <div class="jenkins-button" onclick="showInfo()">SVN
</div>
      <p>Subversion - Centralized version control system.</p>
    </div>
