 <div class="gallery-item">
   <div class="item-text"><strong>Continuous Integration (CI) / Continuous Deployment (CD) : </strong></div>
    <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/ikmedia/backlit.jpg" alt="Photo 3">
    <div class="item-content">
      
        <div class="terraform-button" onclick="showInfo()">Jenkins</div>
       <p>Open-source automation server for building, testing, and deploying applications.</p>
       <div class="terraform-button" onclick="showInfo()">Gitlab</div>
      <p>Integrated continuous integration and delivery built into GitLab.</p>
